---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Carpet Cleaning Brossard | Residential & DIX30 Experts"
  description="Premium carpet and upholstery cleaning in Brossard. Specialists in large residential homes and DIX30 condos using powerful truck-mount technology."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO -->
  <div class="split-hero-container mobile-hero-stack">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT (Hook) -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">CARPET & UPHOLSTERY • BROSSARD</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Expert Carpet Cleaning in Brossard
          </h1>

          <div class="mobile-hero-slideshow fade-in-up delay-050">
            <div class="slideshow-container">
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-40.webp"
              alt="Luxurious sofa cleaning in a Brossard residence"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-vapeur-laval.webp"
              alt="Truck-mount steam technology used in Brossard carpet cleaning"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/resultat-tapis-berbere-propre.webp"
              alt="Immaculate residential carpet after deep cleaning in Brossard"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            </div>
            <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100">
            <h3 class="problem-title">The Challenge of Family Homes:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              In Brossard, from established family neighborhoods to the luxurious new constructions near Quartier DIX30, your carpets and sofas face daily wear and tear: kids, pets, and construction dust. Stubborn stains and allergens become deeply embedded over time.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            Empire Cleaning Group is your trusted partner in Brossard. We utilize the unmatched extraction power of our truck-mount units to restore the original beauty of your carpets, area rugs, and furniture, while eliminating 99% of bacteria and allergens.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Brossard Service)
            </a>
            <button
              onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()"
              class="btn btn-gradient-green"
            >
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Instant Free Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Visual / Slideshow) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-40.webp"
              alt="Luxurious sofa cleaning in a Brossard residence"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-vapeur-laval.webp"
              alt="Truck-mount steam technology used in Brossard carpet cleaning"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/resultat-tapis-berbere-propre.webp"
              alt="Immaculate residential carpet after deep cleaning in Brossard"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="service-main">
          <!-- BENEFIT LIST & SEO CONTENT -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Our Specialized Services for Brossard Residents
            </h2>

            <p>
              To meet the high standards of spacious properties in Brossard, La Prairie, and the DIX30 sector, we offer a complete line of domestic hygiene services:
            </p>

            <ul class="benefit-list" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
              <li>
                <strong>Wall-to-Wall Carpet Cleaning:</strong> Perfect for family rooms, finished basements, and staircases. Our 200°F+ steam dissolves body oils and extracts deeply embedded grit.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Upholstery & Furniture Washing:</strong> Your sofas (fabric, microfiber, or leather) are treated with gentle yet highly effective enzymatic solutions targeting pet stains or wine spills.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Oriental & Area Rug Treatment:</strong> We understand the value of your rugs (wool, silk, synthetic). We balance our chemical logic (pH) to brighten colors safely without the risk of bleeding.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Odor Neutralization (Pet Urine):</strong> No more grocery store perfumes that just mask the issue. We use biological enzymes to actually "digest" uric acid crystals at their source.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Stain Protector (Teflon Guard):</strong> Highly recommended for busy Brossard living rooms, creating an invisible shield that drastically slows down future liquid absorption.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
               <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                🚀 Truck-Mount Technology: The Major Difference
              </h3>
              <p>
                The vast majority of Brossard homes feature private driveways, allowing direct access for our massive truck-mount cleaning units. Why does this matter?
              </p>
              <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                Our gas-powered units generate suction and heat levels that are simply impossible to recreate with portable retail rental machines. You receive an ultra-deep clean and an <strong>ultra-fast drying time (often between 3 and 6 hours)</strong>.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
              <hr class="separator" />
              <h3>Service Tailored to Your Sector</h3>
              <p>
                Whether you live in the "letter" sectors (A, B, C, R, M, P, or V) or in a modern high-rise condo overlooking Quartier DIX30, our mobile crews are frequently dispatched directly on the South Shore, allowing for rapid interventions securely and efficiently.
              </p>
               <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                Read our <a href="/en/tips" style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: bold;">Expert Blog</a> to learn more about our advanced fabric care techniques.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEW SECTIONS: BENEFITS & FAQ -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout" style="display: block;">
        <div class="service-main" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
           
           <!-- ZONES DESSERVIES -->
          <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">Serving All of Brossard and Surrounding Areas</h3>

             <div class="city-group">
              <div class="badges-container">
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sectors A, B, C</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Quartier DIX30 & Surroundings</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sectors R, M, P, V</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sectors O, N, S, T</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 La Prairie (Nearby)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Greenfield Park</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="contact-footer">Book your professional squad today: <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-300" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Frequently Asked Questions — Brossard Cleaning
            </h2>
            <FAQSchema
              faqs={[
                 {
                  question:
                    "I live on the 6th floor of a new condo in Quartier DIX30. Can you clean without a truck-mount?",
                  answer:
                    "Absolutely. For high-rise Brossard condos where our truck hoses cannot reach, we deploy our heavy-duty industrial portable extraction units. They plug into your wall and sink, guaranteeing the same premium hot water extraction results.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "My pets ruined my family sectional sofa with urine. Can you save it?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes, odor removal is our specialty. Instead of merely masking the smell, we inject exclusive enzymes that biologically digest the uric acid crystals embedded deep within your sofa's fibers, permanently destroying the source.",
                },
                {
                   question:
                    "Do you require my home's water supply when using the truck-mount?",
                  answer:
                    "No. Our truck-mounts carry their own large onboard fresh water tanks and haul away the dirty wastewater in a separate sanitary recovery tank.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "How much does carpet cleaning cost in Brossard?",
                  answer:
                    "Pricing varies based on the total square footage, number of rooms, or size of the upholstery. We offer transparent, instant, and free estimates either over the phone or via our online widget tool.",
                }
              ]}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll(".slideshow-container").forEach((container) => {
    const slides = container.querySelectorAll(".slide");
    if (slides.length <= 1) return;
    let currentSlide = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, 4000);
  });
</script>

<style>
  /* Base styles reused from residentiel pages */
  .split-hero-container { background-color: #fff; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; overflow: hidden; width: 100vw; }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; min-height: 80vh; }
  .split-content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .service-cat-badge { text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .split-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .problem-statement { background: #ffffff; border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .cta-group { display: none !important; } }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slideshow-container img.slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    object-fit: cover !important;
    object-position: center !important;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }
  .slideshow-container img.slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .lead-text { max-width: 100%; }
  }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .separator { border: 0; height: 1px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .benefit-list { margin: 2rem 0; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .benefit-list li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .benefit-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: #d32f2f; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: bold; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }
</style>
